subject: Soccer
UEFA Champions League (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Lionel Messi’s three goals helped visiting Barcelona stroll into the knockout phase of the Champions League with a 4-0 rout of Viktoria Plzen on Tuesday in Prague.
